.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-procedures-new 1  "new 0.1.2" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-procedures\-new \- Scaffold a new Rust WASI procedure project
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp procedures new\fR [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-title\fR] [\fB\-\-description\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-lang\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK\fR> <\fIID\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scaffold a new Rust WASI procedure project
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-title\fR \fI<TITLE>\fR [default: ]
Human\-readable title for the procedure
.TP
\fB\-\-description\fR \fI<DESCRIPTION>\fR [default: ]
One\-sentence description of what the procedure does
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-lang\fR \fI<LANG>\fR [default: wasm]
Procedure language/runtime: wasm | python | javascript
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK\fR>
Path to the DKP bundle directory
.TP
<\fIID\fR>
Procedure ID — used as the file stem and Rust crate name (e.g. "macro\-calc")
.SH VERSION
v0.1.2
